msgid "Apache is probably the most widely-known web server, but there are others. Its major opponent is <emphasis role=\"pkg\">nginx</emphasis>, which comes in different packages with different sets of features, like <emphasis role=\"pkg\">nginx-light</emphasis>, <emphasis role=\"pkg\">nginx-full</emphasis>, or <emphasis role=\"pkg\">nginx-extras</emphasis>. Another alternative is <emphasis role=\"pkg\">lighttpd</emphasis>. All of them can offer very good or even better performance under certain workloads or in certain situations, but not all provide the same number of available features and modules."
