msgstr ""

msgid "Note also that the log files created by <command>logrotate</command> need to be readable by everyone, especially AWStats. This is ensured by changing <filename>/etc/logrotate.d/apache2</filename> to include <literal>create 644 root adm</literal> (instead of the default <literal>640</literal> permissions) for example. But please refer to <filename>/usr/share/doc/awstats/README.Debian.gz</filename> for a more extensive documentation about this topic and alternatives."
